---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout>
  {/* HERO */}
  <section class="mb-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Autonomous Rover for Disk Transport</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl">
          Autonomous rover that navigates a constrained course, collects and stacks disk-shaped objects,
          climbs a ramp, and delivers them to a designated drop-off location using camera-based perception
          and closed-loop control.
        </p>

        <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-5">
          <li class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Python</li>
          <li class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">OpenCV</li>
          <li class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Controls (PID)</li>
          <li class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Raspberry Pi</li>
          <li class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Arduino</li>
          <li class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">SolidWorks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      {/* HERO MEDIA */}
      <div class="rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden w-full">
        <video
          class="w-full h-auto"
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          poster="/images/autonomous-rover/hero-poster.jpg"
        >
          <source src="/images/autonomous-rover/hero.webm" type="video/webm" />
          <source src="/images/autonomous-rover/hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          {/* Fallback for ancient browsers */}
          <img
            src="/images/autonomous-rover/rover-hero.jpg"
            alt="Autonomous rover prototype transporting disks"
            class="w-full h-auto"
          />
        </video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* PROBLEM + CONSTRAINTS */}
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Problem & Constraints</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
        <p>
          The rover must autonomously traverse a course (curves, ramp, obstacles), collect and stack disks,
          and drop them off in a specified order under strict size and robustness constraints.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Must fit within a compact volume and remain functional after a short drop test.</li>
          <li>Line-following navigation through curved segments and a ramp.</li>
          <li>Pick up and transport at least two disks; bonus for three.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <img
        src="/images/autonomous-rover/venue-diagram.png"
        alt="Testing venue diagram showing start, pickup, ramp, and drop-off zones"
        class="rounded-lg shadow-sm w-full"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* SYSTEM OVERVIEW */}
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">System Overview</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Raspberry Pi handles high-level compute (vision + navigation decisions).</li>
          <li>Arduino Nano handles low-level actuation (servos, lift, scoop sequencing).</li>
          <li>Drive motors use encoder feedback for consistent speed and repeatability.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <img
        src="/images/autonomous-rover/electronics-schematic.png"
        alt="Electronics and communication schematic for rover control stack"
        class="rounded-lg shadow-sm w-full"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* MECHANICAL */}
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Mechanical Design</h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Chassis</h3>
        <img class="rounded-md mb-3" src="/images/autonomous-rover/cad-overview.png" alt="Assembled rover CAD overview" />
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Modular layered chassis designed for stability, rapid iteration, and serviceability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Basket Lift</h3>
        <img class="rounded-md mb-3" src="/images/autonomous-rover/basket-lift.png" alt="Basket lift crank-slider mechanism" />
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Crank-slider lift raises the basket for controlled placement at the drop-off platform.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Scoop Arm</h3>
        <img class="rounded-md mb-3" src="/images/autonomous-rover/arm-rack-pinion.png" alt="Rack and pinion scoop arm mechanism" />
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          Rack-and-pinion style extension with servo control for disk pickup and unloading.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* CONTROLS */}
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Controls & Autonomy</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>OpenCV line segmentation → lateral error estimate → steering correction.</li>
          <li>PID-based line following and encoder feedback for consistent speed.</li>
          <li>State machine orchestrates: follow line → pickup → incline → drop-off.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <img
          src="/images/autonomous-rover/cv-steering-diagram.jpg"
          alt="Computer vision steering control diagram"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-sm w-full"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/autonomous-rover/state-machine.png"
          alt="State machine diagram for rover behaviors"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-sm w-full"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* RESULTS */}
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Results</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">What worked</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Reliable mechanical pickup and transport when perception loop was stable.</li>
          <li>Consistent drive behavior with encoder feedback.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6">Challenges</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li>Camera lag / warm-up time created inconsistent autonomy performance.</li>
          <li>Integration across tasks was harder than individual task testing.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <figure class="rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden bg-white border">
          <video
            class="w-full h-auto"
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
            preload="metadata"
            poster="/images/autonomous-rover/demo-pickup-poster.jpg"
          >
            <source src="/images/autonomous-rover/demo-pickup.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <figcaption class="px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Pickup demo
          </figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden bg-white border">
          <video
            class="w-full h-auto"
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
            preload="metadata"
            poster="/images/autonomous-rover/demo-dropoff-poster.jpg"
          >
            <source src="/images/autonomous-rover/demo-dropoff.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <figcaption class="px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Drop-off demo
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  {/* LESSONS */}
  <section class="mb-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Lessons Learned & Next Steps</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
      <li>Add sensor redundancy (e.g., IR/ultrasonic) to reduce reliance on camera performance.</li>
      <li>Reduce dependence on platform height by adding a small lift DOF.</li>
      <li>Harden the autonomy pipeline for latency and reboot variability.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</ProjectLayout>